<i>without recognizing that</i>
<i>that's something only God can do.</i>

37
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:11,802
<i>It's one of the strangest stories</i>
<i>ever told.</i>

38
00:06:12,505 --> 00:06:14,973
<i>It's about the great mysteries</i>
<i>of creation:</i>

39
00:06:15,708 --> 00:06:17,471
<i>Life and death.</i>

40
00:06:19,412 --> 00:06:21,846
<i>Prepare yourselves.</i>

41
00:06:22,048 --> 00:06:23,777
<i>You may be shocked,</i>

42
00:06:23,983 --> 00:06:27,111
<i>or even horrified.</i>

43
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:31,779
<i>Few films have had</i>
