<i>Dangerous?</i>
<i>You surprise me.</i>

87
00:16:09,635 --> 00:16:12,729
<i>Haven't you ever wanted</i>
<i>to take a chance?</i>

88
00:16:13,405 --> 00:16:17,239
<i>What if we never went beyond</i>
<i>the limits of the known?</i>

89
00:16:17,776 --> 00:16:21,337
<i>Have you never wished to see</i>
<i>beyond the clouds and stars?</i>

90
00:16:21,613 --> 00:16:24,343
<i>Or to know</i>
<i>what makes trees grow</i>

91
00:16:24,583 --> 00:16:27,677
<i>and changes shadows to light?</i>

92
00:16:30,189 --> 00:16:33,920
<i>But speak like this</i>
<i>and they call you a madman.</i>

93
00:16:36,495 --> 00:16:40,226
<i>Yet if I could answer</i>
<i>just one of these questions... - </i>

94
00:16:40,566 --> 00:16:43,228
<i>what eternity is, for example... - </i>

95
00:16:43,435 --> 00:16:47,565
<i>I wouldn't care</i>
<i>if they called me mad.</i>

96
00:16:47,773 --> 00:16:51,436
<i>You're young,</i>
<i>dazed by your success.</i>

97
00:16:51,643 --> 00:16:54,544
<i>Wake up and see reality.</i>

98
00:16:55,647 --> 00:16:57,877
<i>A demon whose brain... - </i>

99
00:16:58,083 --> 00:17:00,984
<i>You must give it time to develop.</i>

100
00:17:01,186 --> 00:17:03,347
<i>It's a perfect brain, Doctor.</i>

101
00:17:03,956 --> 00:17:07,619
