<i>and play with me?</i>

106
00:17:22,007 --> 00:17:24,407
<i>I have things to do, child.</i>

107
00:17:24,810 --> 00:17:27,244
<i>Play with your kitten.</i>

108
00:17:27,746 --> 00:17:29,646
<i>- Good-bye, Papa.</i>
<i>- Good-bye.</i>

