225
00:34:23,594 --> 00:34:25,585
What is Don José still missing?

226
00:34:28,266 --> 00:34:29,597
His eyes.

227
00:34:29,801 --> 00:34:31,063
Quiet, Isabel.

228
00:34:31,269 --> 00:34:33,362
